Tamasheq: Turkiya tla aǧăriw deɣ krad iɣilan: ejarew wan Aegean deɣ amǝneǧ, Black Sea deɣ afella d ejarew wan Mediterane deɣ aǧus. 
English: Turkey is encircled by seas on three sides: the Aegean Sea to the west, the Black Sea to the north and the Mediterranean Sea to the south.

Tamasheq: Daɣ ănemmănɣi tămeɣan fal aman andukan ɣas beccan as I yussa radar yunayer, tuǧaǧen daw amăn full inin icenga cwaden d-sen. 
English: In the beginning of the war they mostly travelled on top of the sea, but as radar began developing and becoming more accurate the submarines were forced to go under water to avoid being seen.

Tamasheq: Imăzăɣăn ajotnen n Bishkik allăɣen as addinat wi šawănkatnen n-tejje tan ajus arfădnen aššăreɣa. 
English:sometime they were used to attack the enemy's convoys, but they were also used to sink ships.
clean_output: sometime they were used to attack the enemy's convoys, but they were also used to sink ships.

Tamasheq: Turkiya tla aǧăriw deɣ krad iɣilan: ejarew wan Aegean deɣ amǝneǧ, Black Sea deɣ afella d ejarew wan Mediterane deɣ aǧus. 
English: Turkey is encircled by seas on three sides: the Aegean Sea to the west, the Black Sea to the north and the Mediterranean Sea to the south.

Tamasheq: Daɣ ănemmănɣi tămeɣan fal aman andukan ɣas beccan as I yussa radar yunayer, tuǧaǧen daw amăn full inin icenga cwaden d-sen. 
English: In the beginning of the war they mostly travelled on top of the sea, but as radar began developing and becoming more accurate the submarines were forced to go under water to avoid being seen.

Tamasheq: Addălen wǝn tăǧrest ăntani yettiwăzdayen deɣ akalen wi n Afella, imăzzaɣen wi n Italy emhăren deɣ timcecwărin n amăḍal d timădashen tin Olimpik. 
English: Italy was encircled by seas on three sides: the Aegean Sea to the west, the Adriatic Sea to the north and the Adriatic Sea to the south.
clean_output: Italy was encircled by seas on three sides: the Aegean Sea to the west, the Adriatic Sea to the north and the Adriatic Sea to the south.
